The paper discusses the development of bots using natural language processing and machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of APIs and the construction of an API knowledge graph also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions entity recognition, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
